         <div xml:id="gbs333-h65532"> <!-- l3d27prae -->
            <head xml:id="gbs333-h65532-Hd1e100">Praeambulum</head>
            <p xml:id="gbs333-h65532-d1e102">
               <lb ed="#B" n="56"/>DISTINCTIO XXVII. 
      <lb ed="#B" n="57"/>DETERMINATO 
      <lb ed="#B" n="58"/>de duabus 
      theologi<lb ed="#B" n="59" break="no"/>cis uirtutibus: 
      fide<lb ed="#B" n="60" break="no"/>scilicet, &amp; spe: 
      conse<lb ed="#B" n="61" break="no"/>quenter in sex dist. 
      <lb ed="#B" n="62"/>sequentibus agitur de 
      <lb ed="#B" n="63"/>&amp; tertia, quae est 
      chari<lb ed="#B" n="64" break="no"/>tas, hoc ordine. Nam primo determina 
      <lb ed="#B" n="65"/>tur de charitate secundum se, &amp; eius 
      prae<lb ed="#B" n="66" break="no"/>cepto Secundo dist xxviii. de charitatis 
      <lb ed="#B" n="67"/>objecto. Tertio. dist xxix. de charitatis 
      <lb ed="#B" n="68"/>ordine. Quarto dist. xxx. de charitatis 
      <lb ed="#B" n="69"/>amicorum, &amp; iimicorum adinuicem in 
      <lb ed="#B" n="70"/>meriti comparatione. Quinto dist. xxxi. 
      <lb ed="#B" n="71"/>de charitatis creatae permanentia. 
      Sex<lb ed="#B" n="72" break="no"/>to de charitatis increatae sufficientia, 
      <lb ed="#B" n="73"/>Summatur autem sententia textus 
      praesen<lb ed="#B" n="74" break="no"/>tis distinctionis in his tribus 
      conclusio<lb ed="#B" n="75" break="no"/>nibus.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="gbs333-h65532-d1e148">
      ¶ Prima conclusio. Charitas, quae 
      <lb ed="#B" n="76"/>est dilectio una, qua deus propter se, ac 
      <lb ed="#B" n="77"/>in deo, &amp; propter deum proximus 
      dili<lb ed="#B" n="78" break="no"/>gitur in duobus scripturae praeceptis 
      se<lb ed="#B" n="79" break="no"/>cundum diuersa dilio ibilia 
      commenda<lb ed="#B" n="80" break="no"/>tur.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="gbs333-h65532-d1e161">
      ¶ Secunda conclusio. De diligendi 
      <lb ed="#B" n="81"/>modo regula praescribitur diuinitus: ut 
      <lb ed="#B" n="82"/>a nobis toto corde deus: &amp; ad idem, quid 
      <lb ed="#B" n="83"/>amamur nosipsi: diligatur proximus. 
      </p>
            <p xml:id="gbs333-h65532-d1e171">
               <lb ed="#B" n="84"/>¶ Tertia conclusio. Primo praecepto, quod 
      <lb ed="#B" n="85"/>secundum includit: &amp; in secundo 
      inclu<lb ed="#B" n="86" break="no"/>ditur charitatis perfectio, qua deum 
      te<lb ed="#B" n="87" break="no"/>nemur diligere insinuatur: quod 
      tamen<lb ed="#B" n="88" break="no"/>non in uita praesenti: sed in futura 
      ple<lb ed="#B" n="89" break="no"/>nissime consummatur.
    </p>
